<!-- ════════════════ 04 · PLAN VAN AANPAK ════════════════ -->
  <section data-label="Plan van aanpak" class="slide light">
    <div class="glow soft"></div>
    <div class="frame">
      <p class="eyebrow"><span class="num">03</span>Ons plan van aanpak</p>
      <h1 class="title" style="max-width: 1500px;">Van vacature tot versterking<br>in <span class="accent">5 concrete stappen</span>.</h1>

      <div class="steps steps-row" style="margin-top: 60px;">
        <div class="step" style="--c:#4f6cf7">
          <div class="step-head">
            <span class="step-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="9" y1="13" x2="15" y2="13"/><line x1="9" y1="17" x2="13" y2="17"/></svg></span>
            <span class="big-n">01</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Intake &amp; profiel</h4>
          <p><strong>Rol, stack en teamcontext</strong> scherpstellen: wie zoek je écht?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step" style="--c:#f43f5e">
          <div class="step-head">
            <span class="step-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"/><path d="M20 20l-3.5-3.5"/></svg></span>
            <span class="big-n">02</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Sourcing</h4>
          <p>Gericht zoeken in ons netwerk van <strong>voorgekwalificeerd AI-talent</strong>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step" style="--c:#10b981">
          <div class="step-head">
            <span class="step-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/><line x1="10" y1="20" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg></span>
            <span class="big-n">03</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Technische screening</h4>
          <p><strong>Code, modellen en denkwerk</strong>, beoordeeld door practitioners.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step" style="--c:#f59e0b">
          <div class="step-head">
            <span class="step-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><polyline points="16 11 18 13 22 9"/></svg></span>
            <span class="big-n">04</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Matching &amp; cultuurfit</h4>
          <p>Shortlist met kandidaten die passen bij je <strong>team en werkstijl</strong>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step" style="--c:#6366f1">
          <div class="step-head">
            <span class="step-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span>
            <span class="big-n">05</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Plaatsing &amp; opvolging</h4>
          <p>Van getekend contract tot <strong>succesvolle onboarding</strong>, wij blijven betrokken.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="aanpak-choice">
        <span class="ac-lead"><strong>Aanwerven of opleiden?</strong> Vaak is het allebei:</span>
        <span class="ac-opt">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          <span><strong>Nieuw talent</strong> via staffing</span>
        </span>
        <span class="ac-or">en/of</span>
        <span class="ac-opt">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"/></svg>
          <span><strong>Je eigen team</strong> via training</span>
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% set slideNumber = "04" %}
    {% set slideTotal = "09" %}
    {% include "../../shared/chrome.njk" %}
  </section>
